text: Yasmin Khan (born 1977) is a British historian specialising in the history of British India. Yasmin Khan may also refer to: * Yasmin Khan (Doctor Who), a fictional character in the Doctor Who franchise * Yasmin Khan (writer) (born 1981), British food writer ==See also== * Yasmeen Khan (born 1999), Namibian cricketer
title: Yasmin Khan (disambiguation)
